295
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:28,160
All right.

296
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:30,360
Hold still.

297
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,560
Sorry. Sorry.

298
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:42,760
Try not to move so much, okay?

