373
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:26,000
It's not your fault. I'm working
on that. I haven't finished that.

374
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:29,560
I came up here because
there's a problem with the mogwai.

375
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,240
Yeah, what's that?

376
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:34,400
It multiplies with water.

377
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,160
Do you see what I mean?

378
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,840
I don't believe that.

379
00:27:45,040 --> 00:27:46,840
All that from water?
They got wet?

380
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:48,360
Plain water.

381
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:54,560
It's funny.
The new ones aren't like Gizmo.

382
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:56,800
The striped one
seems to be the leader.

383
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,000
You know what?

384
00:27:58,440 --> 00:28:01,360
I'll bet every kid in America
would like one of these.

385
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:04,000
They might replace
the dog as the family pet.

386
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,240
Think about it.

387
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:18,360
The Peltzer Pet.

388
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:23,560
This could really be the big one.

389
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,960
Barney, who did this to you?

390
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,840
