00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:47,800
Giz, you want some?

496
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,000
Do you want some chicken?

497
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:18,200
That's it, good buddy.
Call it a night.

498
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:57,680
Can 't you see?
